data.description:
If you are looking for a lovely home in Yukon with tall ceilings, plenty of natural light, and a little extra privacy... this is it!

-Brand new roof with Class 4 shingle and decking installed in 2023
-New gutters 2023
-Fresh exterior paint 2023
-New garage doors with remote 2023
-HVAC system upgraded in 2023
- Convenient access nearby to all major highways & the turnpike
-Close to restaurants, grocery stores, & shopping in Yukon
-Walking distance to Yukon HS
-Backs up to wooded area with no neighbor behind
-Corner lot 
-No HOA
